Oral English Teachers Needed at Heze University 

The contract starts in February or September. 
Workload: 16 hours of classes per week; 
Monthly salary: 6000-7000RMB; 
Air ticket allowances: 4000-8000 RMB for one-year contract; 
Free furnished apartment provided on campus; 
Free access to water, electricity and internet; 
Requirements: 
1) Bachelor degree or higher; Doctorate with higher payment; 
 2) TEFL/ TESOL/ CELTA certificate holder; 
3) Native or Official English speakers from USA, UK, Australia, Canada , New Zealand, Ireland etc; 
4) Prefer 2+ years of experience teaching; 
5) Age: 25-63 years old; 
